  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators previously reported that colonoscopy with a transparent retractable
      extension (TRE) device improved the adenoma detection rate without affecting intubation and
      withdrawal times. On the other hand, colonoscopy using narrow band imaging (NBI) is expected
      to lead to higher rate s of adenoma detection. The investigators compared the effects of TRE
      device on colorectal adenoma detection with those of NBI.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
